<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gold-n">gold <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡəʊld/    美 /ɡoʊld/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>金；黄金制品；金币：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After trying hard, I got a job in a gold mine.
几经周折，我在一家金矿找到了工作。</p><footer>人教① – 5</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>金色；金黄色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun shone on the gold of her hair.
太阳照在她金黄色的头发上。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[非正式用语] 金质奖章；金牌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>win an Olympic gold
获得奥运金牌</p></div></div>